    slug: 'navigating-parental-grief-supporting-children-bereavement',
    title: 'Navigating Your Own Grief While Supporting Children Through Family Bereavement: A Parent\'s Guide',
    category: 'Mental Health',
    excerpt: 'Parents, learn strategies to process your own grief while effectively supporting your children through family bereavement. Find compassionate guidance and practical tips.',
    metaDescription: 'Parents, learn strategies to process your own grief while effectively supporting your children through family bereavement. Find compassionate guidance and practical tips.',
    readTime: 7,
